overview_description.description: Anew Climate is a company that operates in the environmental consulting, greentech, and renewable energy industries. The company is a result of the combination of Element Markets and Bluesource. Anew Climate focuses on delivering impact in a decarbonizing economy and works within natural climate solutions. The company has also made acquisitions, such as entities managed by The Forestland Group, and has purchased forestland in northern Michigan. Anew Climate's services include supplying renewable natural gas to FuelCell Energy.

about_short_description.short_description: Anew Climate provides a range of environmental products, carbon reduction solutions, credit development, and climate services.

product.name: Epoch™ Evaluation Platform
product.description: A platform combining satellite monitoring, AI, and data collection for accuracy in credit generation and additionality substantiation.

product.name: RNG Marketing and Credit Generation
product.description: Services for biomethane marketing, including generation to monetization of environmental credits for various sectors.

product.name: Natural Climate Solutions
product.description: Development and management of forest carbon and nature-based projects for conservation and carbon credit generation.

product.name: Emission Credits
product.description: Generation, management, and monetization of air quality emission credits for compliance in over 100 markets.

product.name: Anew Canada Low Carbon Fuels
product.description: Services for generating, aggregating, and monetizing low carbon fuel credits in Canada's Clean Fuel Programs.

product.name: Climate Solutions as a Service (CSaaS)
product.description: Full-service support for achieving carbon neutrality, net-zero, and climate goals through expert guidance and services.
